urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:1.627#By the time he finished, the ivory-armed goddess
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:1.628#Was smiling at her son. She accepted the cup from him.
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:1.629#Then the lame god turned serving boy, siphoning nectar
