urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:2.11#And to it he spoke these feathery words:
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:2.12#"Go, deadly Dream, along the Greek ships
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:2.13#Until you come to the hut of Agamemnon,
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:2.14#And deliver this message to him exactly:
