urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:2.60#"Listen, my friends. A dream from Zeus
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:2.61#Came to me last night in my sleep. It looked
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:2.62#Just like Nestor, same face, same build,
