urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:2.75#Think it over.' The dream said all this
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:2.76#And off it flew, and I awoke from a sweet sleep.
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:2.77#We'd better move if we're going to get the men in armor.
