urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:14.184#That was as white as the sun, and bound
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:14.185#Lovely sandals on her oiled, supple feet.
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:14.186#When everything was perfect, she stepped
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:14.187#Out of her room and called Aphrodite
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:14.188#And had a word with her in private:
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:14.189#"My dear child, will you do something for me,
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:14.190#I wonder, or will you refuse, angry because
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:14.191#I favor the Greeks and you the Trojans?"
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:14.192#And Zeus' daughter Aphrodite replied:
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:14.193#"Goddess revered as Cronus' daughter,
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:14.194#Speak your mind. Tell me what you want
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:14.195#And I'll oblige you if I possibly can."
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:14.196#And Hera, with every intention to deceive:
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:14.197#"Give me now the Sex and Desire
