urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:14.204#I'm going to see them and try to resolve
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:14.205#Their endless quarrel. For eons now
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:14.206#They've been angry and haven't made love.
