urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:14.231#She took Sleep's hand, and said to him:
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:14.232#"Sleep, lord of all, mortal and immortal,
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:14.233#If ever you've listened to me before,
