urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:14.242#Sweet Sleep answered her:
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:14.243#"Goddess revered as Cronus' daughter,
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:14.244#If this were any other of the gods eternal
