urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:14.274#Sleep's mood brightened at this. He said:
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:14.275#"Swear by the inviolable water of Styx,
urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.sl:14.276#One hand on fertile Earth and the other
